label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"鸡输卵管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"疼痛不安","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":32,"text":"蛋壳上往往带有血迹","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 鸡输卵管炎，病禽主要表现为疼痛不安，产出的蛋其蛋壳上往往带有血迹。病因比较复杂，是威胁养鸡业健康发展多发病之一。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"卵巢炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"输卵管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"腹膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":38,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":50,"end":54,"text":"卵泡变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":62,"end":65,"text":"红褐色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":69,"text":"灰褐色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"破裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":75,"end":85,"text":"破裂于腹腔中的蛋黄液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":86,"end":89,"text":"味恶臭","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":92,"end":96,"text":"卵泡皱缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":94,"end":96,"text":"皱缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":97,"end":102,"text":"形状不整齐","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":104,"end":107,"text":"金黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":108,"end":110,"text":"褐色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":111,"end":114,"text":"无光泽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":121,"end":125,"text":"肠道粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":123,"end":125,"text":"粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":126,"end":137,"text":"输卵管有黄白色干酪样物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":130,"end":133,"text":"黄白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":78,"end":80,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":92,"end":94,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":121,"end":123,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":126,"end":129,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":43,"text":"腹膜发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"腹膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 卵巢炎、输卵管炎及腹膜炎是鸡，特别是产蛋鸡的一种常见病，临床上以卵巢、输卵管、腹膜发炎为特征，严重时卵泡变形、充血、出血，呈红褐色或灰褐色，甚至破裂，破裂于腹腔中的蛋黄液，味恶臭，有时卵泡皱缩，形状不整齐，呈金黄色或褐色，无光泽，病情稍长时，肠道粘连，输卵管有黄白色干酪样物。病因比较复杂，是威胁养鸡业健康发展多发病之一。

label: [{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"细菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":23,"text":"白痢沙门氏菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":29,"text":"副伤寒杆菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":74,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":78,"end":83,"text":"损伤输卵管","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":80,"end":83,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":95,"end":99,"text":"维生素A","labels":["drug"]},{"start":100,"end":101,"text":"D","labels":["drug"]},{"start":102,"end":103,"text":"E","labels":["drug"]},{"start":108,"end":112,"text":"输卵管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":116,"end":120,"text":"输卵管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":113,"end":115,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":126,"end":131,"text":"输卵管脱垂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":129,"end":131,"text":"脱垂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":126,"end":129,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":132,"end":134,"text":"难产","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 禽舍卫生条件太差，泄殖腔被细菌（如白痢沙门氏菌、副伤寒杆菌、大肠杆菌等）污染而侵入输卵管；或饲喂动物性饲料过多，产蛋过大或产双黄蛋，有时蛋壳在输卵管中破裂，损伤输卵管；或产蛋过多、饲料中缺乏维生素A、D、E等均可导致输卵管炎。家禽患输卵管炎，往往会引起输卵管脱垂、难产等。

text: 1、鸡群外观一切正常,但产蛋无高峰期

text: 3、输卵管内有大小不等水泡,大的有600多毫升,小的有几毫升.积水是清凉,无色,透明,无味的液体.有些鸡输卵管无积水,但有盲端或输卵管狭窄或无输卵管口

text: 4、大多数病鸡卵泡发育正常.有的鸡腹腔内有6-7个成熟的卵子,但是没有完整功能的输卵管,无法产蛋,其他器官无异常

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"疼痛不安","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":26,"text":"产出的蛋其蛋壳上往往带有血迹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":36,"text":"输卵管内经常排出黄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":37,"end":44,"text":"白色脓样分泌物","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":36,"text":"黄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":58,"text":"污染肛门周围及其下面的羽毛","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":63,"text":"产蛋困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":76,"end":78,"text":"发热","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":84,"end":88,"text":"痛苦不安","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":89,"end":93,"text":"呆立不动","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":94,"end":98,"text":"两翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":96,"end":98,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":99,"end":103,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":101,"end":103,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":106,"end":113,"text":"腹部靠地或昏睡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":131,"end":136,"text":"输卵管破裂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":115,"end":122,"text":"炎症蔓延到腹腔","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":134,"end":136,"text":"破裂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":115,"end":117,"text":"炎症","labels":["disease"]},{"start":126,"end":129,"text":"腹膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":138,"end":144,"text":"卵黄性腹膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"病禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"肛门","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":95,"end":96,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":99,"end":101,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":106,"end":108,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":120,"end":122,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":131,"end":134,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病禽主要表现为疼痛不安，产出的蛋其蛋壳上往往带有血迹。输卵管内经常排出黄、白色脓样分泌物，污染肛门周围及其下面的羽毛，产蛋困难。随着病情的发展，病禽开始发热，而后热退，痛苦不安，呆立不动，两翅下垂，羽毛松乱，有的腹部靠地或昏睡，当炎症蔓延到腹腔时可引起腹膜炎，或输卵管破裂引起卵黄性腹膜炎。

text: 剖检病变主要是卵泡变性、变形、充血、出血、坏死或萎缩；输卵管水肿、变粗，内有大量分泌物，腹膜发炎、充血、浑浊，严重的卵泡掉入腹腔，形成卵黄性腹膜炎，肠道与腹膜发生粘连或腹腔肠道、脏器发生粘连；腹腔积有浑浊液体，恶臭或有黄白色干酪样物质。当表现卵黄性腹膜炎时，输卵管壁会变薄，内有异形蛋样物，表面不光滑，切面层呈轮状。

label: [{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":11,"end":19,"text":"改善禽舍卫生条件","labels":["control"]},{"start":20,"end":26,"text":"合理搭配日粮","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":36,"text":"适当喂些青绿饲料","labels":["control"]},{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"细菌感染","labels":["disease"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]}]
text: 平时注意加强饲养管理，改善禽舍卫生条件，合理搭配日粮，并适当喂些青绿饲料。由于本病大多由细菌感染引起，因此，痊愈后的家禽不宜留作种用。

label: [{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"隔离检查","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"蛋卵","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":36,"text":"向泄殖腔内灌入润滑剂类","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"润滑剂类","labels":["drug"]},{"start":62,"end":67,"text":"高锰酸钾液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":69,"end":72,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":73,"end":78,"text":"输卵管下部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":80,"end":82,"text":"冲洗","labels":["control"]}]
text: 1、发病后应立即隔离检查，如有蛋卵停留在泄殖腔内，向泄殖腔内灌入润滑剂类，促使将卵排出体外。然后用注射器吸入温水或者低浓度的高锰酸钾液注入泄殖腔和输卵管下部进行冲洗，

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"抗菌药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"输卵管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"阿莫西林","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"头孢菌素类药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"环丙沙星","labels":["drug"]},{"start":38,"end":48,"text":"抗病毒病中药惠农博沙","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 2.抗菌药：治疗输卵管炎，如阿莫西林（头孢菌素类药或环丙沙星）等。若同时兼用抗病毒病中药惠农博沙，效果更好。
